data.title: Venezuelan home food! Delicious!!!!!
data.text:
This place did not dissapoint, everything is so fresh and home made and ths service is top notch!

Salad options include variety of greens, toppings, protein, seeds, dressing, etc so you can custom your salas to your hearts desire! Which I love! 

Sides and paninis are also varied, sides being typical Venezuelan empanadas, tequeños (fried pastries to die for), baked brie and cheese platters. So one can come every day and have different options! 

They also have a soup of the day, freshly prepared and today was a thai spicy soup 👍🏻. 

I cannot say enough good things about this amazing jewel, it's just fresh and homey. Plus a zillion options for teas and snoothies! And the staff is sooooooo super nice!

Enough said, can't wait to come back soon!

FYI salad size is BIG so share!
